## <a id="reqs"></a> Requirements

Zettaset XCrypt Archive for BBR has the following requirements:

+ Java v1.7.0 or greater

+ Java Cryptography Extension (JCE) Unlimited Strength Juridiction Policy files

+ libselinux-python and cryptsetup-luks

+ 3rd Party, KMIP-compliant Key Manager or Zettaset's Virtual Enterprise Key Manager (V-EKM). To download and install vEKM, contact our [sales team](mailto:sales@zettaset.com).


